Company Overview of Centaur Mutual Funds Trust - Centaur Total Return Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Centaur Mutual Funds Trust - Centaur Total Return Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Centaur Capital Partners, L.P. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. It invests directly and through derivatives such as call options to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in dividend paying value stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations. It employs fundamental analysis focusing on factors such as companies with positive (or projected positive) revenue or profit trends, healthy balance sheet characterized by ample cash relative to debt, efficient working capital management, high or...
Centaur Mutual Funds Trust - Centaur Total Return Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Centaur Capital Partners, L.P. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. It invests directly and through derivatives such as call options to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in dividend paying value stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations. It employs fundamental analysis focusing on factors such as companies with positive (or projected positive) revenue or profit trends, healthy balance sheet characterized by ample cash relative to debt, efficient working capital management, high or increasing liquidity, or other metrics that indicate the company’s ability to withstand unexpected shocks, reinvest in the business and improve its business prospects and circumstances, strong free cash flow generation, powerful and sustainable competitive advantages, management team that operates the business well and has a sound strategy to build it over time, one which allocates capital wisely to enhance shareholder value and has high integrity and policies (e.g., compensation structures) that do not significantly dilute shareholders’ ownership to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Total Return Index and the Dow Jones U.S. Select Dividend Total Return Index. It was formerly known as Tilson Investment Trust - Tilson Dividend Fund. Centaur Mutual Funds Trust - Centaur Total Return Fund was formed on March 16, 2005 and is domiciled in the United States.
