Centaur Mutual Funds Trust - Centaur Total Return Fund Key Developments

Centaur Total Return Fund Declares Annual Distributions, Payable on December 12, 2016
Dec 8 16
Centaur Mutual Funds has announced that the Centaur Total Return Fund will declare annual capital gains distributions for 2016. The fund is projecting to pay approximately $0.33 per share in Short Term Capital Gains and $0.27 per share in Long Term Capital Gains, for a total distribution of approximately $0.60 per share. The dividend is payable on December 12, 2016, with the record date of December 8, 2016. The ex-dividend date is December 9, 2016.


Centaur Total Return Fund Announces Annual Distributions for 2015 Payable on December 14, 2015
Dec 8 15
Centaur Mutual Funds, the adviser of the Centaur Total Return Fund declared that the fund will release an annual capital gains distributions for 2015 of about USD 0.64 per share total. All shareholders of record date on 10 December 2015 will be paid the dividend on 14 December 2015 and the ex-dividend date is 11 December 2015. Also, the fund is projecting to pay short term capital gains of USD 0.41694 per share and long term capital gains
of USD 0.22917 per share, for a total distribution of the above mentioned amount.


