Welcome
This website is under the operation of Centaur Financial Services Limited, a Cyprus Investment Firm regulated by the Cyprus Securities and Exchange Commission.

Centaur Financial Services Limited (“Centaur”) is a fund management group, providing discretionary portfolio management services to high net worth individuals, institutions, provident funds and listed investment trusts.
Centaur manages individually tailored portfolios for high net worth individuals, institutions and mutual funds. In addition, Centaur structures fixed income tailor-made products for institutional investors and high net worth individuals. Through its eighteen-year history Centaur has consistently delivered above-average returns using proprietary research to identify undervalued assets in a variety of industries and markets. The research and administration is controlled from our office in Nicosia Cyprus, but investors typically choose to hold their assets with UK regulated brokers and custodians.

